{
  "stem": "1400.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just talked to some of them through the fence, but it-- they-- doctors doing some terrible experiments on them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we couldn't really talk too much, because the guards on the tower, they didn't let us go close to the barbed wire, even.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You approached the barbed wire too close, they were free to shoot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was like open season on Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't have to account for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Several.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Several.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if somebody-- it happened that somebody met some relations across, and he run over to the-- to the-- or a friend-- he run over, not thinking, to the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About three foot from the barbed wire-- which at night, it was electrified.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the daytime, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they run over to the street for distance, and started talking excitedly, recognizing somebody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The guard gunned him down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's not once-- many times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the other side, in that Russian encampment, these Russian prisoners of war were ordered to work outside on the field, outside from Auschwitz, somewhere on the field, taking apart damaged airplanes for Nazi air force-- taking out usable parts.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At one time, five of them escaped, and their freedom didn't last too long.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were brought back, two of them, and shot dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the other three, right in the middle of the camp, they were hanged, and a place card was placed on their chest, 'I escaped.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I am here again.'",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is one of the-- to go back a little bit, when I arrived to the camp-- this was in the following months-- and I described what was around me.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
